cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.GT, cs.CL

This paper presents a dataset of StarCraft replays that can be used for a wide variety of machine learning tasks such as strategy classification, inverse reinforcement learning, imitation learning, forward modeling, partial information extraction, and others. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Game Theory (cs.GT), and Computation and Language (cs.CL) as it involves natural language processing for partial information extraction.
